{"tid":1448001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:47.000Z","uid":77535,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"27f9907b6b9e3604cdcc3da0a6f66c3bd2f6cad8","tid":1448001,"uid":77535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=0dd44ae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=d6efa7ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"6c773c53529e171f2db32837dab96c656299ed69","tid":1448001,"uid":77535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1c34acd457f0d6e10638090b7ca407f7663141e","tid":1448001,"uid":77535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"126a5ffa94fa15091098f028e0e0f79625ef0655","tid":1448001,"uid":77535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"992259c64e8120755af414ff7456bf33d5dd8e86","tid":1448001,"uid":77535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30f1270b69b4c9a0a5dd9798c9754d1da0b743d2","tid":1448001,"uid":239416,"like":0